<img src="logo.png">
<p>Welcome to CrimeSpi's official website! We hope you enjoy it!<br>Note: Click <a href="gmap.html">here</a> or click "GOOGLE MAP", which is at the top, for our official page that displays the crimes.</p>
<p>Our Google Map is devoted to bring you crimes using an API from <a href="data.police.uk">data.police.uk</a>.<br>
Our steps to bringing you accurate crime details:<ol><li>We retreive the Year & Month you want to display crimes in, as well as your <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;postcode.<li>We convert the postcode, using an API, to Latitude and Longitude co-ordinates.<li>We update a bar chart, stating crimes of what type are in your area<li>We update the map by changing the center to your postcode's co-ordinates, and <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;adding the crimes around your area.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;We do not just pust <i>every</i> crime on the map and just change the co-ordinates,<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;but we add the crimes around your area, therefore saving you loading time & file size.</ol><br>
